**Wade Brown** — *interjecting (OOC)*
> "Finders keepers!"

**Valphine** — *in-character warning*
> "there's some Talosian cultists, heading this way, and… You know, starting a ritual that's pretty dangerous."

**GM** — *Vorga's response*
> "She, she looks at you and says, do you have proof?"

**Valphine** — *presenting evidence*
> "Yeah. That's no… Can we talk? a local ranger named the Falcon, who, You know, had, seen them, you know. you know, staging an area east of here called the Woodland Manse. One of their rituals, Got a couple hours to the north here, just a few hours ago."

**GM** — *Vorga's reaction*
> "Okay. She's, like, going, alright. She looks at you very carefully and says, Mmm. Well… We fight."

**Valphine** — *following up*
> "You want to help defend this location?"

**GM** — *Vorga's military reasoning*
> "She looks around and says, if Talosian come to kill, this best place to defend everyone here. She looks around and you realize there's, like, 20 or so non-combatants."

