**[Switching to Common — The Dragon Revelation]**

**Vukradin** — *asking Valphine what was said*
> "Oh, were they displaced by the dragon?"

**Valphine** — *confirming*
> "Sounds like it."

**GM** — *Prutha weighing in*
> "Prutha says, yes."

**Valphine** — *to the courtyard*
> "dragon that you killed."

**Vukradin** — *announcing*
> "We killed the dragon."

**GM** — *the courtyard's reaction*
> "They look… they… everybody stares at you in disbelief. You killed Dragon?"

**Vukradin** — *confirming*
> "Yep, I got this."

**GM** — *Vorga processing the news*
> "She looks at you, alright? She looks at you, goes, There's… Dragon is dead. That home is now free to go back?"

**Vukradin** — *confirming*
> "Yeah, you can go back."

**Valphine** — *adding a caveat*
