**Vukradin** — *announcing Aid*
> "I'm gonna cast Aid. Everybody add 5 hit points."

**Wade Brown** — *clarifying*
> "5 temporary."

**Vukradin** — *correcting*
> "Nope, it's not temporary hit points. It's your maximum, your HP maximum. Or 8 hours, goes up by 5."

**Wade Brown** — *noting the difference*
> "So, semi-temporary. No, it is, because it can be healed."

**Vukradin** — *on spell level*
> "I will not do the third level, though. I'm not gonna… only second level aid."

**Vukradin** — *accounting remaining resources*
> "You know, I've got… I've burned 2 level 1s and 2 level 3s."

**Valphine** — *adding*
> "I also have sending, but, That would be my last third level spell."

